{"about_the_game":"All the same, all the time. Day in, day out. But maybe there is more, if you just look close enough ... and remember.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Recollect your surroundings</h2>Bring the forgotten wonders of this beautiful world back to your attention.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804610/extras/world.gif?t=1736009966\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Varied gameplay</h2>Rediscover fascinating things like the stars, flowers and trees in playful experiences.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804610/extras/natural.gif?t=1736009966\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Two game modes</h2>Face the many threats these wonders are facing in the optional second &quot;fragile mode&quot;.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804610/extras/fragile.gif?t=1736009966\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Accessibility</h2>Adjust the game to your likings through many settings, i.e. change the difficulty seamlessly at any time without getting punished for it.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804610/extras/settings.gif?t=1736009966\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Many wonderful things to discover in hand-crafted, diverse experiences<br></li><li> Casual, accessible gameplay<br></li><li> Two game modes: Natural (relaxed &amp; wholesome) / Fragile (challenging &amp; concerning)<br></li><li> Atmospheric silhouette artstyle<br></li><li> Emotional, magical soundtrack<br></li><li> Short playtime of about 1-2 hours<br></li><li> Playable with mouse &amp; keyboard, controller or just using the mouse</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Something to make you dream...","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1804610/226282d9426b39376584988f6345924278068e83.jpg"},{"name":"Somethin